---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome to Adiatma's Blog Corner!</h1>
			<p>Hello and thank you for stepping into my digital realm! I'm 
				your host and the creator of this little space on the internet.</p>

			<strong>About Me</strong>
			<p>I'm a Software Engineer enthusiast with a passion for Software Engineering & DevOps. 
				Here, you'll find a collection of my thoughts, experiences, and creative endeavors. 
				Whether you stumbled upon this site intentionally or by happy accident, 
				I'm thrilled to have you here!</p>
			
			<strong>What to Expect</strong>
			<p>This site is my canvas, and I love painting it with a diverse palette of Software Engineering.</p>

			<p>Thank you for being here!</p>

		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
